{"tid":1216641,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[不安] 見到有人提議炸IFC","createTime":"2019-06-13T10:38:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T11:00:54.000Z","uid":29388,"like":76,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"49847c8fd9e4cb7679f1002e57abed10fa0811ae","tid":1216641,"uid":29388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:38:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gdhrebb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgdhrebb.jpg&h=2d6111ed&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/jordteam/posts/10157112580960460\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjordteam%2Fposts%2F10157112580960460&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmWa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=8a17dd2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/jordteam/posts/10157112580960460</a><br />\n<br />\n有朋友喺IFC做野, 好擔心佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8735ed13f82ba27833513d02762e0c84ab552a0","tid":1216641,"uid":157522,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:41:48.000Z","msg":"8月17日晚21时许，民警根据群众举报，在滨湖区某公司内抓获违法行为人孙某（男，江苏射阳人，滨湖区某公司员工）。经核查，8月15日17时08分，孙某利用手机软件客户端<span style=\"color: red;\">在某群内散布有关恐怖言论</span>。<br />\n<br />\n孙某的行为已构成<span style=\"color: red;\">虚构事实、扰乱公共秩序</span>。根据《中华人民共和国治安管理处罚法》第二十五条第一项之规定，滨湖公安分局已于8月18日对其作出行政拘留五日的处罚决定。<br />\n<br />\n警方提示<br />\n<br />\n网络空间是公共空间，网络社会是法治社会。<span style=\"color: red;\">编造传播网络谣言严重破坏社会公共秩序</span>，严重影响社会和谐稳定，特别是编造传播恐怖袭击谣言，制造混乱和恐慌，危害极大，公安机关将依法严厉打击。希望广大网民不造谣、不信谣、不传谣，共同维护健康和谐的网络环境和社会秩序。<br />\n<br />\n和諧呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c1ca3b40c7631648e1d6acfcdabeada267bb94","tid":1216641,"uid":224533,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:43:05.000Z","msg":"藍絲個腦究竟